# (spf13/viper THIS — Axis 13 expands to 2 variants) → expected R631
# TS-Node=65 → expected R632 90th language.  This is the 2nd of 3
# leader bumps in the current segment.
#
# This completion EXPANDS Axis 13 (CONFIGURATION FILES) to TWO
# documented variants — symmetrically distributed across Rust
# (config-rs R629) and Go (spf13/viper R630).  TS-Node Axis 13
